    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌾 <strong>Farm Management</strong><br>Plant fruits, vegetables, cereals, and raise various animals (cows, chickens, goats, pigs, alpacas...) to produce goods like milk, eggs, and wool.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐔 <strong>Breeding &amp; Genetics</strong><br>Breed your animals to pass down powerful genes, improve their stats, and try to obtain rare golden animals with special powers and visuals!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>Turn-based Animal Battles</strong><br>Form a team of 4 animals, customize their stats, and engage in strategic PvP battles! Train your team daily and climb the rankings!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏡 <strong>Expand and Personalize</strong><br>Unlock vehicles, expand your land, build barns and greenhouses, and boost your production efficiency.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌦️ <strong>Dynamic Seasons and Weather</strong><br>The seasons and weather influence your farm and your animals’ strength in battle — plan ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌟 <strong>Events, Rankings, and Community</strong><br>Join weekly and monthly competitions, complete seasonal events, and climb the leaderboards as the best farmer or the strongest battler.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐾 <strong>Relaxing but Competitive</strong><br>Play at your own pace: focus on farming, breeding, or PvP battles — your farm evolves even when you’re offline!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐣 Why try Farmer Toon?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Free, with no pay-to-win</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Rich yet accessible gameplay</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Ideal for fans of strategy, simulation or collecting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >✅ Developed with passion by a solo creator 💛</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎁 Welcome bonus: A bonus of 50% plant growth speed for 2 hours offered to new players to get you started faster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
